      "created_at": "2022-01-18T19:51:21.923Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hmm, yes this sounds like a problem.  One thing you can do which obviously is not ideal is forget about power match and just use the pedals on zwift and the trainer with our app.  If you have fairly consistent offset you could just adjust your workout a little modified and record with zwift and ultimately it would be kind of like power match.  The other option is to get a NPE Cable device and connect it to Ant+ and this would give you second bluetooth channel.</p>",
