      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-01-19T00:11:56.815Z",
      "cooked": "<p>If you use the TrainerDay app to control your trainer, you can\u2019t pair the trainer as a controllable in Zwift. But normally you should be able to connect to it as a Power source and just read power from it.<br>\nAnd I would be surprised if the Assioma\u2019s don\u2019t support 2 BLE devices. Did a quick search but can\u2019t find it right away.<br>\nif you let Zwift scan for devices, isn\u2019t it finding at least one of them as a power source?</p>",
