      "created_at": "2022-01-19T04:00:12.042Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t know if this generally works, but on my Samsung Android phone I simultaneously use Bluetooth with the Zwift Companion app, and Trainer Day. Perhaps it works since it\u2019s a single device hence it treats it as a single Bluetooth connection?</p>\n<p>As MedTechCD mentions, you need to pair with Zwift first and disable the controllable power in Zwift.</p>",
