      "cooked": "<p>I have seen cases where I can connect 2 devices to one source and I believe that is a BLE5 feature but I don\u2019t know how to repeat this now. But my experience is like yours that once trainer is connected to one source it can\u2019t be connected to another because yes it all comes through as a single device with multiple services.</p>",
