      "cooked": "<p>Yes, if you read about BLE 5 it supports multiple channels but I am not sure how this all works.  Android 8+ supports BLE 5 and iOS 11+ but I assume the devices themself need to be BLE 5 and maybe that is the same thing you are talking about.</p>",
