      "created_at": "2022-01-19T21:35:23.908Z",
      "cooked": "<p>The only way round it for me is to run zwift on a phone. That way I can pair it via ant+ as apposed to just BLE via the companion app.</p>\n<p>I think this is a lot of faff. I\u2019ll just wait for TD to add ant+ to the workout app. That would be by far the easiest solution.</p>",
