      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/rkid84/{size}/912_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-01-23T23:09:53.968Z",
      "cooked": "<p>To confirm this works.</p>\n<p>I can use my phone to connect TD via Bluetooth to my pedals, HRM and trainer using powermatch and also the companion app on Zwift to record power.</p>\n<p>I did have to connect the devices via the companion app first. It didn\u2019t work if I tried to connect TD first.</p>\n<p>One more thing, you have to disable background battery optimisatiom for the companion app otherwise it\u2019ll just go to sleep\u2026that\u2019s if you are using android. No idea about apple.</p>",
