      "created_at": "2022-01-24T04:56:39.890Z",
      "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/rkid84\">@rkid84</a> Glad to hear it works. Yes, generally you need to connect Zwift first, unpair the power control (so that it doesn\u2019t fight TD).</p>\n<p>I haven\u2019t had the Zwift Companion App go to sleep on me (I believe its notification helps with this?) but what you\u2019re saying is good advice.</p>",
